Package: restraintsfalls
Title: Physical Restraint Use and Falls in Nursing Homes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ivan", "Marino", , email = "ivan.marino@upipa.tn.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Research compendium for the analysis of the association between
    physical restraint use and falls in nursing homes in the province of
    Trento, Italy. Uses longitudinal quality monitoring data from the
    Indicare Salute Lab system (2016-2025).
